			Ok, one more post to clarify the previous fellow's posting.  The gauntlets he is speaking of are the Wu gauntlets which are a tailoring item.  Recipe is....<BR>
 1. Heady Kiola<BR>
 2. Raw silk gloves<BR>
 3. Greater Lightstone<BR>
 4. Vial of Viscous Mana<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
Note, I did not put exact numbers since I don't know the exact numbers.  I'll let you know if I find them.  Also to reiterate....Neither the spell itself, or the Viscous Mana which is the result increases mana regen.  Think about it, wouldn't that make Clarity pretty useless when you get it at level 29?  The gauntlets are NOT a blacksmithing item, but a tailoring one.  And lastly, on a side note, Griffawns hit harder then you'd think for their level.  =P  Hope this all helps, and I'll see you on Bertoxx.<BR>

